<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
    <title>About Us - Your Photography Studio Name</title>
    <style>
      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #333;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #666;
      }
      .signature {
        text-align: right;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #888;
      }
      nav {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px 20px;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      nav ul li {
        display: inline;
        margin-right: 20px;
      }

      nav ul li a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/nav.ejs') %>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p>
        Welcome to Your Photography Studio Name, where moments are captured,
        memories are preserved, and stories are told through the lens of
        creativity.
      </p>
      <p>
        At Your Photography Studio Name, we believe in the power of photography
        to transcend time and evoke emotions. Established with a passion for
        visual storytelling, our studio is dedicated to capturing the essence of
        life's most precious moments, from weddings and family portraits to
        corporate events and beyond.
      </p>
      <p>
        Led by an experienced team of photographers with a keen eye for detail
        and a commitment to excellence, we strive to deliver exceptional quality
        in every image we capture. Our approach blends artistic vision with
        technical expertise, ensuring that each photograph is a true reflection
        of the unique beauty and authenticity of our subjects.
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond just taking pictures, we pride ourselves on building genuine
        connections with our clients, understanding their vision, and exceeding
        their expectations. From the initial consultation to the final delivery
        of images, we prioritize clear communication, professionalism, and a
        personalized experience tailored to each individual's needs.
      </p>
      <p>
        With a dedication to continuous learning and innovation, we stay at the
        forefront of industry trends and techniques, always seeking new ways to
        push the boundaries of creativity and storytelling. Whether it's
        capturing the grandeur of a scenic landscape or the intimacy of a candid
        moment, we approach every project with passion, professionalism, and a
        commitment to excellence.
      </p>
      <div class="signature">
        <p>
          Thank you for considering Your Photography Studio Name for your
          photography needs.
        </p>
        <p>Warm regards,</p>
        <p>Your Name</p>
        <p>Your Photography Studio Name</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
